detail_desc: Running tights in fast-drying, breathable functional fabric with elastication and a concealed drawstring at the waist. Key pocket at the back, ventilating mesh sections, reflective details and a zip at the hems.

Shirt dress in a viscose weave with a narrow collar, button placket, gathered seam at the shoulders and long sleeves with narrow, buttoned cuffs. Seam at the waist with a concealed zip in the side. Unlined.
Set with a bracelet and necklace of chunky steel curb chain with a trigger clasp. Bracelet circumference 19.5 cm. Total necklace length 48 cm.
Bra strap extenders in different colours. 2.5x7.5 cm.

Oversized shirt in crisp cotton poplin with a pointed collar, concealed button placket and yoke with a pleat at the back. Dropped shoulders, long, wide sleeves with wide, buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem. Longer at the back.
Blouse in woven fabric with a round neck and collar with ties at the front. Gathered yoke at the back, buttons down the front, long sleeves with wide, buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem.

Knee-length dress in a woven viscose blend with a small, gathered stand-up collar, covered buttons at the top, long, wide raglan sleeves and cuffs with covered buttons. Asymmetric seam at the waist and a gently flared skirt. Unlined.
Strappy top in soft jersey made from a silk and cotton blend with a slightly deeper neckline front and back.

Long-sleeved shirt in woven fabric with an easy-iron finish. Cutaway collar, French front, yoke at the back, cuffs with adjustable buttoning, and a rounded hem. Slim Fit with narrow shoulders and a tapered waist.
Baby Exclusive. Leggings in soft cotton jersey with an adjustable, elasticated waist.
V-neck strappy tops in soft, organic cotton jersey, one ribbed.
Push-up tights that lift and shape with an elasticated waist. 70 denier.
Trainer socks in a soft, fine-knit cotton blend with elasticated tops.
Blouse in a viscose weave with a small, lace stand-up collar, button placket and lace section at the top. Long sleeves with elasticated cuffs, and a rounded hem. Longer at the back.
Long-sleeved jersey top with a matching skirt in tulle. Top with reversible sequins at the front (sizes 1½-2Y with normal sequins). Lined skirt with an elasticated waist.
5-pocket, slim-fit jeans in washed, superstretch, flexible denim for maximum mobility. Adjustable, elasticated waist, a zip fly and button, and narrow hems.

Suit trousers in a softly draping weave with an extended waistband, concealed hook-and-eye fastening and an adjustable tab with a metal fastener at the sides. Zip fly with a concealed button, side pockets, welt back pockets with a button, and slightly shorter legs with creases and turn-up hems. Slim fit that is close-fitting at the thighs, knees and ankles to create a fitted silhouette.
Leggings in soft, stretch denim with an elasticated waist, fake front pockets, real back pockets and seams at the knees.

Shoulder bag in sturdy imitation leather with a suede flap, metal fastener and adjustable metal chain shoulder strap. One large outer compartment at the front and one inner compartment. Fabric lining. Size 4.5x16.5x22 cm.
Sleeveless, A-line dress covered in sequins.
Hipster briefs in organic cotton jersey with a low waist, lined gusset and cutaway coverage at the back.
Two-strand hairband with braids in imitation suede and elastic at the back.
Cap in printed cotton jersey with a sweatband inside and concealed elastication at the back.
Metal rings. Three smooth, one with stripes and one signet ring.
Leggings in soft, stretch jersey with a glittery elastic waistband.
V-neck blouse in a crinkled weave with 3/4-length sleeves with flounced cuffs, and a flounce at the hem.
Narrow metal bracelet. Width 0.5 cm.
3/4-length jeans in stretch cotton denim with a zip fly and button, fake front pockets, real back pockets and straight legs with short slits in the sides.
Double-breasted coat in felted fabric with a collar and decorative stitching front and back. Decorative flaps at the waist, pockets in the side seams and a single back vent. Lined.

Short, faux shearling-lined parka in a cotton weave with a faux fur-trimmed hood, stand up collar and zip and wind flap with concealed press-studs down the front. Patch front pockets with a flap and press-stud and concealed side pockets. Covered elastication and a tab with an adjustable fastening at the cuffs. Concealed drawstring at the waist and hem, and a small back vent. Lined.
Shirt in a printed cotton weave with a collar, buttons down the front, a yoke at the back, long sleeves with buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem.
Hat in a ribbed wool-blend knit containing some cashmere with a faux fur pompom on the top.

Trenchcoat in woven fabric with a soft, brushed finish, notch lapels with decorative buttons, a loose yoke with a zip at the front, and concealed press-studs down the front. Detachable belt with a metal buckle at the waist , a tab and metal fastener at the cuffs, zipped side pockets and a single back vent. Unlined.
Pyjamas with a jersey top and flannel bottoms. Top with a motif on the front and long sleeves with ribbed cuffs. Bottoms with an elasticated drawstring waist, side pockets and ribbed hems.
Ankle boots in imitation leather with pointed toes, covered heels and a concealed zip in one side. Recycled polyester linings and imitation leather insoles. Heel 5 cm.
Imitation leather sandals with adjustable foot straps with metal buckles, an adjustable heel strap with a hook and loop fastening, and a loop at the back. Moulded rubber soles, fluted underneath.
Top in a soft, rib-knit viscose blend containing some linen with short sleeves and slits in the sides of the hem. Slightly longer at the back.
Cargo trousers in stretch twill with a high waist, zip fly and button, fake front pockets, real back pockets and flap leg pockets with concealed press-studs.
Tunic in a cotton weave with a collar, button placket, yoke at the back and buttoned cuffs. Detachable tie belt and a rounded hem.

Straight-cut shirt in imitation leather with a pointed collar and covered buttons down the front. Long puff sleeves, cuffs with covered buttons, a seam at the waist and across the sleeves, and a rounded hem.

Jeggings in superstretch denim with a low waist, zip fly and button, and back pockets. The cotton content of the jeggings is partly recycled. Push up – denim with a superstretch function that showcases the body’s physique.
Trainers with elasticated lacing at the front and a loop at the back. Fabric linings and insoles and rubber soles.
Short, fitted skirt in stretch velour with decorative embroidery on the front and concealed elastication at the waist. Unlined.
Shorts in an airy cotton and linen weave with diagonal side pockets and elastication, a short frill trim and decorative bow with tassels at the waist.

3/4-length sports trousers in lightweight, fast-drying functional fabric with an elasticated waist and side pockets. Tapered legs with hole-patterned side stripes, shaping seams at the knees and ribbed hems.
Off-the-shoulder blouse in a cotton weave with a V-neck and foldover edge with a button at the top. Buttons down the front and at the cuffs.
Braided bracelets in various designs. Adjustable length.
Metal earrings with a rectangular plate at the top and a rod and hoop-shaped pendant. Length 5.7 cm.
Long top in sweatshirt fabric with a terry appliqué on the front, drawstring hood, ribbed cuffs and a raw-edge hem. Soft brushed inside.
T-shirt in soft, printed cotton jersey.
Cap with a motif, covered button on top and an adjustable plastic fastener at the back.
Short dress in softly draping Tencel™ lyocell denim with a collar, press-studs down the front and a detachable tie belt at the waist. Short sleeves, open chest pockets and short slits in the sides.
Leaf-patterned tights with an elasticated waist.
Jacket in a soft linen blend with notch lapels and a tie at the front. Flap front pockets and long sleeves with a slit at the cuffs. Lined.
Short, 5-pocket skirt in washed denim with a button fly and frayed, raw-edge hem.
Cargo joggers in stretch cotton twill with an elasticated drawstring waist, side pockets and flap back and leg pockets with press-studs. Fake fly, shaping seams at the knees and ribbed hems.
Baby Exclusive. Polo-neck collar in soft, rib-knit wool.
Cold shoulder blouse in a viscose weave with narrow adjustable shoulder straps, elastication and a flounce at the top, long sleeves with elastication at the cuffs, and a smocked hem.
Jersey fancy dress costume with an accessory, a print motif on the front and a hook and loop fastening at the back.
Block-coloured jumper in a soft rib knit with low dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Cardigan in fine-knit cotton with buttons down the front and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Jumper in a soft, fine knit with long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Suit trousers in a crêpe weave with a high waist, hook-and-eye fasteners and zip fly. Side pockets and straight, wide legs with creases.
Straight-cut, sleeveless blouse in woven fabric with a sheen. Round neck, a pleat at the front, buttons at the back and a straight-cut hem with short slits in the sides. Longer at the back.
Metal hoop earrings. Two different sizes: 4.5 cm and 7.5 cm.
Fitted corset top in jersey with a sheen. Wide shoulder straps and a square neckline front and back. Shaping seams front and back, and a rounded hem.
Straight-cut top in soft jersey made from a modal and cotton blend with short wide sleeves in woven fabric with broderie anglaise and a scalloped trim.
Ankle boots with pointed toes, covered heels, elastic gores in the sides and a loop at the back. Fabric linings. Heel 3.5 cm.
Jumper in a soft jacquard knit with a ribbed polo neck, long raglan sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.

Calf-length, one-shoulder dress in glittery tulle made from recycled polyester. One shoulder strap with a decorative bow and beaded metal buckle. Draping at the top, a concealed zip in one side and a gathered seam at the waist for a softly draping effect. Jersey lining.
Blucher shoes in shiny imitation leather with lacing at the front. Fabric linings and insoles and rubber soles that are patterned underneath. Heel approx. 3.5 cm.
Wide, straight-cut T-shirt in cotton jersey with a yoke front and back, short sleeves with print stripes and a rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back.

Ankle-length trousers in woven fabric with a high waist with pleats and a detachable belt. Zip fly, concealed hook-and-eye fasteners, pockets in the side seams, fake welt back pockets and legs with creases.

Set with a long-sleeved top and shoulder bag in soft cotton jersey. Top with a reversible sequin motif on the front (sizes 1½-3Y with normal sequins). Slightly longer and rounded at the back. Bag with a sequined motif on the front, a hook and loop fastening at the top and a narrow shoulder strap with a hook and loop fastening at one end. Lined. Size of bag approx. 11.5x13 cm.
Long-sleeved Henley shirt in ribbed organic cotton jersey with a button placket and ribbed cuffs.

Boxy-style, long-sleeved jumper in a rib knit containing some wool. Polo neck with large metal and imitation pearl buttons, and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. The polyester content of the jumper is recycled.
Short, fitted turtleneck top in soft jersey.
Short coat in sturdy faux fur with a large collar, a concealed hook-and-eye fastening at the front and discreet pockets in the side seams. Lined.
Top in soft viscose jersey with a lace yoke, short raglan sleeves and a straight-cut hem.
Short-sleeved sports top in airy, organic cotton jersey with slits in the sides. Slightly longer at the back.
